**Overview**

This dashboard shows Misconfiguration overview related to the Prisma Cloud Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics of passed/failed scanned policies and overall passed/failed assets from Prisma Cloud.

It should overall distribution by asset type and cloud type. It also specifically shows failing assets and asset types along with their distribution.
It fetches new updates every 24 hours by default.

**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/prisma_cloud/overview)**
